# Dr. Antoine Cloutier-Blais
## Associated Clinic
[Meraki Clinic](@/blog/clinics/meraki.md)
## Attitude of Doctor
## Pre-Prescription Requirements
Respondent One: 
* He needed **one appointment** to get a prescription
* He said he wasn't interested in fertility treatment, and that was accepted without question
## Prescription Practices
Respondent One:
* He started at 0.02g subQ and increased to 5mg on 1 per cent gel
* He asked to be in the upper half of the male range
* He thought that the reasoning given for administration method and choice of dosage was very comprehensive
## Monitoring
* He got blood tests every 3 to 4 months when starting, and now gets them every 5 to 7 months
